{"title":"什么是伴随矩阵？","slug":"what-is-adjoint-matrix","date":"2017-10-13T12:44:46.000Z","updated":"2020-08-31T21:48:25.785Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/what-is-adjoint-matrix.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["/assets/blogimg/伴随矩阵.jpg","/assets/blogimg/cat1.jpg","/assets/blogimg/cat2.jpg","/assets/blogimg/cat3.jpg"],"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/hint.css/2.4.1/hint.min.css\"><img src=\"/assets/blogimg/伴随矩阵.jpg\">\n<h2>首先我们来看如何得到<a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?ie=UTF-8&wd=%E4%BC%B4%E9%9A%8F%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">伴随矩阵</a>:</h2>\n~~1.设A=（a<sub>ij</sub>）为n阶方阵\n2.A<sub>ij</sub>是|A|在（i，j）上a<sub>ij</sub>的代数余子式\n3.则全部由代数余子式组成的n阶方阵为A的伴随矩阵A~~\n\n\n<h2>我们来弄清楚几个专有名词：</h2>\n~~|A|：n阶方阵的n阶行列式，行列式是一个数;\na<sub>ij</sub>的元余子式：n阶行列式去除i行j列剩下的部分，记作M<sub>ij</sub>;\na<sub>ij</sub>的代数余子式：A<sub>ij</sub>=(-1)<sup>i+j</sup>M<sub>ij</sub>;~~\n\n<p>现在知道什么叫伴随矩阵了吗？不知道点这里—&gt;<a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?ie=UTF-8&wd=%E4%BC%B4%E9%9A%8F%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.baidu.com/s?ie=UTF-8&amp;wd=伴随矩阵</a></p>\n<h2>放图时间：</h2>\n<img src=\"/assets/blogimg/cat1.jpg\">\n<img src=\"/assets/blogimg/cat2.jpg\">\n<img src=\"/assets/blogimg/cat3.jpg\">\n","more":"<img src=\"/assets/blogimg/伴随矩阵.jpg\">\n<h2>首先我们来看如何得到<a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?ie=UTF-8&wd=%E4%BC%B4%E9%9A%8F%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">伴随矩阵</a>:</h2>\n~~1.设A=（a<sub>ij</sub>）为n阶方阵\n2.A<sub>ij</sub>是|A|在（i，j）上a<sub>ij</sub>的代数余子式\n3.则全部由代数余子式组成的n阶方阵为A的伴随矩阵A~~\n\n\n<h2>我们来弄清楚几个专有名词：</h2>\n~~|A|：n阶方阵的n阶行列式，行列式是一个数;\na<sub>ij</sub>的元余子式：n阶行列式去除i行j列剩下的部分，记作M<sub>ij</sub>;\na<sub>ij</sub>的代数余子式：A<sub>ij</sub>=(-1)<sup>i+j</sup>M<sub>ij</sub>;~~\n\n<p>现在知道什么叫伴随矩阵了吗？不知道点这里—&gt;<a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?ie=UTF-8&wd=%E4%BC%B4%E9%9A%8F%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.baidu.com/s?ie=UTF-8&amp;wd=伴随矩阵</a></p>\n<h2>放图时间：</h2>\n<img src=\"/assets/blogim